        <sponsor name-id="M001191">Mr. Murphy of Florida</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="C000266">Mr. Chabot</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HWM00">Committee on Ways and Means</committee-name>
